<entry>How to Move Up</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry><list id="fs-idm261653056" list-type="bulleted">
<item>Love what you do, which entails first figuring out who you are.</item>
<item>Never stop learning about new technologies and new skills that will help you build a successful career.</item>
<item>Try to get international experience even if it is only a short stint overseas.</item>
<item>Create new business opportunities—they could lead to a promotion.</item>
<item>Be really terrific at what you’re doing now, this week, this month.</item>
</list></entry>
